.TH "vmw_validation_res_validate" 9 "vmw_validation_res_validate" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_validation_res_validate \- Validate all resources registered with the validation context.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vmw_validation_res_validate
.BI "(struct vmw_validation_context *ctx "  ","
.BI "bool intr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
The validation context.
.IP "intr" 12
Whether to perform waits interruptible if possible.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Before this function is called, all resource backup buffers must have
been validated.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success, -ERESTARTSYS if interrupted,
negative error code on failure.
